title: Are some people extra universal aliens? - Quora

response.answer_text: Are some people extra universal aliens? I dont know. There are quite a lot of others like me, who originate in other places in this universe, I dont recall ever meeting or hearing about a being from another universe, although my instinct tells me it is possible to move between universes. Quite a talent I guess it would be.
Yes. Asket, Nera, Yanarara, and Zefenatpaneach are a few. They don’t live here; they only visit.
